::Zardus::

Standing up, Zardus sees Sickle, frowning as he reads the words. He looks at 
them, not sure what to make of it.

Zardus walks out of the conference room, hoping the words would follow. It 
wasn't a good habit to talk to air with bots from other factions in the room.
